&lt;h2 id="step-2-discover-devices"&gt;Step 2: Discover Devices&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Find Shelly devices on your network:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Adding Your First Device</title><link>http://localhost:1313/shelly-cli/docs/getting-started/first-device/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>http://localhost:1313/shelly-cli/docs/getting-started/first-device/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;This guide provides detailed instructions for adding your first Shelly device to the CLI.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="prerequisites"&gt;Prerequisites&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Before you begin, ensure you have:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shelly CLI installed (&lt;a href="http://localhost:1313/shelly-cli/docs/getting-started/installation/"&gt;Installation Guide&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A Shelly device powered on and connected to your WiFi&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The device IP address or mDNS hostname&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Device authentication credentials (if password-protected)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="finding-your-device"&gt;Finding Your Device&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="option-1-use-discovery"&gt;Option 1: Use Discovery&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The easiest way to find your device:&lt;/p&gt;



&lt;div class="expressive-code"&gt;
 &lt;figure class="frame is-terminal not-content"&gt;
 &lt;figcaption class="header"&gt;
 &lt;span class="title"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/figcaption&gt;
 &lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;div style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;
&lt;table style="border-spacing:0;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;;width:100%"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;shelly discover&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This scans your local network using mDNS and returns all discovered Shelly devices.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>